elems.code: { all c: Course | no p: Professor | p in c.teaches and p in c.enrolled }
{ no c: Course, p: Professor | p in c.teaches and p in (Professor - Student) }
{ all c: Course | no p: Professor | c in p.teaches and p in c.enrolled }

{
	
  	
	all disj p1, p2: Professor | 
  	p2 not in teaches.(p1.teaches) 
  	
	or 
  	p2 not in enrolled.(p1.teaches) 
  	
  
   	all p : Professor | no teaches.(p.teaches) & enrolled.(p.teaches)
  	
  	
  	
}
{ all p : Professor | no (p.enrolled & p.teaches) }
{ all c: Course | no p: Professor | c in p.teaches and c in p.enrolled }
{ all p : Professor | no ((Professor - Student - p).enrolled & p.teaches) }
{ all p : Professor & Student | no ((Professor & Student - p).enrolled & p.teaches) }
{ all p : Professor | no (((Professor & Student)-p).enrolled & p.teaches) }

{
   
   all p: Professor | 
      all c: p.teaches | 
         no p2: Professor | c in p2.enrolled
         and not (c in p.enrolled)
         and not (p in Student and c in p.enrolled)
}

{
   
   all p: Professor | 
      all c: p.teaches | 
         no p2: Professor | c in p2.enrolled
         and not (c in p.enrolled)
         and no s: Student | s in Professor and c in s.enrolled
}
{ no c: Course, p: Professor | c in p.teaches and p in (Professor - Student) }
